set on our property.

26
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:10,160
Maybe, he wants to
reign our kingdom.

27
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,110
He can take it all
if that's what he wants.

28
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:16,050
Do we give up on our rights

29
