and we are no exception.

35
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:44,040
Just the way
a fish inhales water

36
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:46,110
and then exhales it.

37
00:02:47,110 --> 00:02:49,020
Neither does it accepts
water into its system

38
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,920
nor does it reject it.

39
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:59,890
In the same way, human beings
own a piece of land while alive

40
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:03,080
but eventually,
have to leave it behind.

41
00:03:03,980 --> 00:03:05,850
We were born in the jungle

42
00:03:06,110 --> 00:03:08,090
and are now,
ruling this kingdom.

43
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,120
Maybe, in future,
we go back to the jungle.

44
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,920
This kingdom isn't ours
for a lifetime

45
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:23,080
but our pride is

46
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:27,890
and so is our self-confidence.

47
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:40,020
We can't let go of our pride
and self-confidence

48
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:41,940
in the wake of a battle.

49
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:44,850
It's not just about
the kingdom, My King.

50
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,080
I fear

51
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:52,020
that if in this game
we play to protect our honour

52
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,850
we will lose our piousness.

53
00:03:55,110 --> 00:03:57,090
And if we protect our piousness

54
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,950
we will lose everything
that we have.

55
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:10,890
If we protect our piousness,
Panchali

56
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,820
we will be able to get back
all that we lose.

57
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:16,010
Even if we lose this kingdom

58
00:04:16,810 --> 00:04:19,020
we will build a new kingdom
somewhere else.

59
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:24,860
But I can't refuse
uncle Dhritarashtra's order.

60
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:33,980
Uncle

61
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,780
I will definitely go
to Hastinapur.

62
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:40,820
And if uncle Dhritashtra
orders me

63
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:42,920
I will surely gamble.

64
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,790
They have entered this place

65
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:21,760
just the way a fawn

66
00:05:21,910 --> 00:05:25,860
enters the mouth of a python.

67
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:35,720
They have come with their pride

68
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,910
just to have it

69
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:40,950
squashed by us.

70
00:05:41,980 --> 00:05:45,790
Their arrival was inevitable,
my child.

71
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:52,820
When you make the right move

72
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,910
you can compel others

73
00:05:57,910 --> 00:06:01,720
to give

74
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:04,810
in to your wish.

75
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:11,660
Let's go and welcome them.

76
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:17,820
While welcoming the
sovereign king, Yudhisthir

77
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,680
don't forget

78
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:23,810
to be humble
to him.

79
00:06:27,810 --> 00:06:29,880
For the last time.

80
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:05,720
May you be happy always.

81
