Or

118
00:11:57,660 --> 00:12:00,670
do we need to apologise
to you

119
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,780
if something lacks
in our hospitality?

120
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:14,640
King!

121
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,770
Please come in,
if you wish to.

122
00:12:19,730 --> 00:12:21,770
We have arranged a grand
welcome for you

123
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:26,640
at the court of Hastinapur.

124
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:44,770
Shall we, dear?

125
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,560
Let's go, uncle.

126
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:50,740
Welcome.

127
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,800
Queen...

128
00:13:07,660 --> 00:13:11,610
If you wish, we can first
visit the family deity's temple.

129
00:13:11,730 --> 00:13:13,770
After which, you can
enter the court.

130
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,600
As you say,
Queen mother.

131
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,540
Is the snake letting go
of its venom

132
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:41,770
or is it the venom that's
forsaking the snake?

133
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:46,580
Why are we being given
so much respect?

134
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:50,680
A sacrificial lamb is fed well
before it could be sacrificed.

135
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,540
We should stay alert, brother.

136
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:04,500
Don't worry, Nakul.

137
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:07,610
As long as Grand Sire
Bhishma is with us

138
00:14:07,730 --> 00:14:09,610
he won't let any harm
befall us.

139
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:15,670
Let's proceed.

140
00:14:44,730 --> 00:14:45,710
What happened, Sahdev?

141
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:48,540
I'm getting
a sense of foreboding.

142
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:52,630
Today, this court is going
to witness an injustice

143
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:56,510
that has never taken place
in the history of mankind.

144
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:04,400
Don't worry, Sahdev.

145
00:16:06,430 --> 00:16:11,380
Grand Sire, Sir Drona,
uncle Dhritarashtra

146
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,570
and uncle Vidur are here.

147
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:17,480
