Grand Sire, you look worried.

163
00:18:11,850 --> 00:18:12,830
Yes, Vidur.

164
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:18,730
I'm worried about the fact
that in this game of gambling

165
00:18:20,690 --> 00:18:22,830
Shakuni is surely
going to cheat.

166
00:18:25,820 --> 00:18:28,660
Looking at the splendour
of Indraprastha

167
00:18:30,690 --> 00:18:33,720
Duryodhan is envious.

168
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:39,590
He wants
the kingdom of Pandavas

169
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:43,790
by hook or crook.

170
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:52,560
The reason for my worry
is the same, Grand Sire.

171
00:18:56,790 --> 00:18:57,760
Grand Sire

172
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:01,790
please try and stop this game
of gambling from taking place.

173
00:19:02,690 --> 00:19:06,660
My rights and my powers
have been subdued, Vidur.

174
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:12,760
A throne made of sand
remains intact

175
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:19,530
until someone sits on it.

176
00:19:21,490 --> 00:19:22,560
But Pandavas

177
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:26,530
with their hard work

178
00:19:26,620 --> 00:19:28,570
