be defeated so badly

186
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:08,530
that they would never be able
to come to terms with it.

187
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:19,430
Their kingdom, their army

188
00:20:19,620 --> 00:20:21,460
their property...

189
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:25,670
Take it all
away from them, uncle.

190
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:27,520
Is that it?

191
00:20:30,490 --> 00:20:31,620
My children

192
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:35,460
I'm going to

193
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:39,620
crush their pride.

194
00:20:42,690 --> 00:20:44,560
Those who don't

195
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:47,460
have a reason

196
